00:01:51,144 --> 00:01:53,980
Killua: Right.
Let’s do one final check.

23
00:01:54,014 --> 00:01:55,148
( Map beeping )

24
00:01:55,182 --> 00:01:57,251
Once we’re in,
gon and I will head

25
00:01:57,284 --> 00:02:00,187
up the central stairway
